\section{
  \title{Integrations}

  \link{Vault Integration with Concourse}{https://github.com/pivotalservices/concourse-pipeline-samples/tree/master/concourse-pipeline-patterns/vault-integration} by \link{Pivotal Services}{https://github.com/pivotalservices}.
  Describes Vault configurations for integration with a BOSH-deployed Concourse server.

  \link{Secure credential automation with Vault}{https://github.com/pivotal-cf/pcf-pipelines/blob/master/docs/vault-integration.md} by \link{Pivotal Services}{https://github.com/pivotalservices}.
  Examples of using Vault for credentials management in Concourse pipelines

  \link{CredHub Integration with Concourse}{https://github.com/pivotal-cf/pcf-pipelines/blob/master/docs/credhub-integration.md}
  This guide provides samples of deployment manifests and pipelines for the
  integration of a BOSH-deployed Concourse server with CredHub

  \link{Concourse integration with UAA}{https://github.com/pivotalservices/concourse-pipeline-samples/tree/master/concourse-pipeline-patterns/uaa-authentication} by \link{Pivotal Services}{https://github.com/pivotalservices}.
  A guide on securing teams in Concourse using UAA as an identity provider
}

